---
layout: page
title: Code Snippets
description: 'Ready-to-use code snippets for common problems that can be copied and pasted.'
keywords:
  - code
  - open-source
  - github
permalink: /snippets/
eleventyImport:
  collections:
    - snippets
---

{% styles "components/list" %}

{% renderTemplate "md" %}
These are small code snippets usually extracted from more in-depth articles so
they can be easily retrieved and referenced. It should be possible to copy and
paste them with minor effort.
{% endrenderTemplate %}

{% assign snippets = collections.snippets | reverse %}

<ul class="List NoListMarker">
  {% for snippet in snippets %}
    {% if snippet.data.date %}
      {% assign date = snippet.data.date | time %}
    {% endif %}
    {% assign vt_source = snippet.url | slugify %}

    {% render "list_item.liquid"
      primary: snippet.data.title,
      secondary: date,
      href: snippet.url,
      vt_source: vt_source,
      tags: snippet.data.tags
    %}
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
